        "S": "Cut 2 pounds chicken breasts into 1-inch chunks and add to the marinade bag. Press out excess air, seal, and refrigerate for 1-3 hours. Do not marinate longer than 3 hours or the soy sauce will make the chicken overly salty and the texture mushy."
